arChildNodes.szComment:
VIGO stands guard by the GATED MINE ENTRANCE, arms crossed in irritation. 
The COIN TRINKET from Vhenard hangs from his arm. 
THE PLAYER approaches and addresses him. 
They are interrupted as a small rock falls onto Vigo from offscreen (possibly thrown by NEYRELLE).
We see NEYRELLE for the first time, standing atop a boulder. She jumps down and approaches Vigo.
Neyrelle’s brow furrows. Her memory unsettles her.
Vigo and Neyrelle look up to see the PLAYER approaching. Neyrelle gives Vigo a challenging look, before turning to face the Player.
